# Local tests before PR (FamilyTree)

Never open or update a PR into **dev** or **prod** until local gates are green.

Required local commands (from repo root):

```powershell
dotnet format GMO.FamilyTree.sln --verify-no-changes
npm run lint:js
dotnet test GMO.FamilyTree.sln
```

If `GMO.FamilyTree.Web.exe` is locked by a running site, stop that process first, then re-run tests. Fix failures before `git push` / `gh pr create`. CI watch is a backstop only.
